<bibRefCitation author="Day, J. H." box="[606,718,1418,1441]" pageId="64" pageNumber="65" pagination="1 - 67" refId="ref60832" refString="Day, J. H. (1951) The polychaet fauna of South Africa, 1. The Intertidal and estuarine Polychaeta of Natal and Mozambique. Annals of the Natal Museum, 12, 1 - 67." type="journal article" year="1951">Day, 1951</bibRefCitation>
